Not my husband.

121
00:05:04,638 --> 00:05:06,306
Please, no.

122
00:05:06,348 --> 00:05:08,266
[ Sobbing ]

123
00:05:08,308 --> 00:05:11,812
♪♪♪

124
00:05:11,853 --> 00:05:14,606
Lisa: Everything
alright, Don?

125
00:05:14,648 --> 00:05:16,650
Yeah.
J‐Just a little tired.

126
00:05:16,650 --> 00:05:18,401
