127
00:05:18,443 --> 00:05:19,653
I'm gonna have to get
a little shut eye.

128
00:05:19,653 --> 00:05:21,321
I'm sorry.
‐Oh, of course.

129
00:05:21,363 --> 00:05:23,490
I put fresh sheets
on your old bed.

130
00:05:23,490 --> 00:05:25,575
You remember the way,
don't you?

131
00:05:25,617 --> 00:05:27,244
Of course.
[ Chuckles ]

132
00:05:27,285 --> 00:05:29,329
♪♪♪

133
