least three quarts, maybe more.

178
00:07:30,450 --> 00:07:31,701
Wow.
Big project, huh?

179
00:07:31,743 --> 00:07:33,119
Yeah.

180
00:07:33,161 --> 00:07:35,080
Septic tank.

181
00:07:35,121 --> 00:07:42,462
♪♪♪

182
00:07:42,504 --> 00:07:49,969
