238
00:10:44,644 --> 00:10:46,312
I'll keep you posted.

239
00:10:46,312 --> 00:10:47,814
[ Tires squealing ]

240
00:10:47,814 --> 00:10:51,109
♪♪♪

241
00:10:55,196 --> 00:10:55,238
.

242
00:10:56,573 --> 00:10:56,656
♪♪♪

243
